{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":873,"text":"It was just an ordinary Saturday."},{"time":3320,"text":"My dad was outside mowing the lawn,"},{"time":5560,"text":"my mom was upstairs folding laundry,"},{"time":7840,"text":"my sister was in her room doing homework"},{"time":10000,"text":"and I was in the basement\nplaying video games."},{"time":13080,"text":"And as I came upstairs\nto get something to drink,"},{"time":15440,"text":"I looked out the window"},{"time":16680,"text":"and realized that there was something\nthat I was supposed to be doing,"},{"time":20000,"text":"and this is what I saw."}]},{"cues":[{"time":23880,"text":"No, this wasn't\nmy family's dinner on fire."},{"time":27000,"text":"This was my science project."},{"time":30240,"text":"Flames were pouring out,"},{"time":31720,"text":"smoke was in the air"},{"time":32960,"text":"and it looked like our wooden deck\nwas about to catch fire."},{"time":36200,"text":"I immediately started yelling."},{"time":38040,"text":"My mom was freaking out,"},{"time":39560,"text":"my dad ran around to put out the fire"},{"time":41680,"text":"and of course my sister\nstarted recording a Snapchat video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45840,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":47760,"text":"This was just the beginning\nof my team's science project."},{"time":51480,"text":"My team is composed of me\nand three other students"},{"time":54160,"text":"who are here in the audience today."},{"time":56280,"text":"We competed in FIRST LEGO League"},{"time":58320,"text":"which is an international\nLEGO robotics competition for kids,"},{"time":61880,"text":"and in addition to a robotics game,"},{"time":63760,"text":"we also worked\non a separate science project,"},{"time":66160,"text":"and this was the project\nthat we were working on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68880,"text":"So the idea for this project all started"},{"time":70880,"text":"when a few months earlier,"},{"time":72160,"text":"a couple of my teammates\ntook a trip to Central America"},{"time":75000,"text":"and saw beaches littered with Styrofoam,"},{"time":77520,"text":"or expanded polystyrene foam."},{"time":80040,"text":"And when they came back\nand told us about it,"},{"time":82200,"text":"we really started thinking about the ways\nin which we see Styrofoam every day."},{"time":85920,"text":"Get a new flat-screen TV?"},{"time":87560,"text":"You end up with a block of Styrofoam\nbigger than the TV itself."},{"time":91080,"text":"Drink a cup of coffee?"},{"time":92560,"text":"Well, those Styrofoam coffee cups\nare sure going to add up."},{"time":95760,"text":"And where do all these items go\nafter their one-time use?"},{"time":99160,"text":"Since there aren't any good\nexisting solutions for used Styrofoam,"},{"time":102600,"text":"almost all of them\nend up right in the landfill,"},{"time":105160,"text":"or the oceans and beaches,"},{"time":106520,"text":"taking over 500 years to degrade."},{"time":109240,"text":"And in fact, every year, the US alone"},{"time":111480,"text":"produces over two billion\npounds of Styrofoam,"},{"time":114160,"text":"filling up a staggering\n25 percent of landfills."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117360,"text":"So why do we have these ghost\naccumulations of Styrofoam waste?"},{"time":121040,"text":"Why can't we just recycle them\nlike many plastics?"},{"time":124400,"text":"Well, simply put, recycled\npolystyrene is too expensive"},{"time":127840,"text":"and potentially contaminated,"},{"time":129440,"text":"so there is very little market demand\nfor Styrofoam that has to be recycled."},{"time":133680,"text":"And as a result, Styrofoam\nis considered a nonrenewable material,"},{"time":137240,"text":"because it is neither feasible\nnor viable to recycle polystyrene."},{"time":141600,"text":"And in fact, many cities across the US"},{"time":144200,"text":"have even passed ordinances"},{"time":145640,"text":"that simply ban the production\nof many products containing polystyrene,"},{"time":149280,"text":"which includes disposable utensils,"},{"time":151360,"text":"packing peanuts, takeout containers"},{"time":153560,"text":"and even plastic beach toys,"},{"time":155720,"text":"all products that are very useful\nin today's society."},{"time":158720,"text":"And now France\nhas become the first country"},{"time":160920,"text":"to completely ban all plastic utensils,"},{"time":163200,"text":"cups and plates."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165280,"text":"But what if we could keep using Styrofoam"},{"time":167720,"text":"and keep benefiting\nfrom its cheap, lightweight, insulating"},{"time":171480,"text":"and excellent packing ability,"},{"time":173240,"text":"while not having to suffer\nfrom the repercussions"},{"time":175600,"text":"of having to dispose of it?"},{"time":177320,"text":"What if we could turn it into\nsomething else that's actually useful?"},{"time":180840,"text":"What if we could make\nthe impossible possible?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":184400,"text":"My team hypothesized that we could use\nthe carbon that's already in Styrofoam"},{"time":189000,"text":"to create activated carbon,"},{"time":190720,"text":"which is used in almost\nevery water filter today."},{"time":193480,"text":"And activated carbon works\nby using very small micropores"},{"time":197120,"text":"to filter out contaminants\nfrom water or even air."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200840,"text":"So we started out\nby doing a variety of heating tests,"},{"time":204040,"text":"and unfortunately, we had many failures."},{"time":207640,"text":"Literally, nothing worked."},{"time":210200,"text":"Besides my dad's grill catching on fire,"},{"time":212480,"text":"most of our samples\nvaporized into nothing,"},{"time":215160,"text":"or exploded inside expensive furnaces,"},{"time":217600,"text":"leaving a horribly sticky mess."},{"time":220440,"text":"In fact, we were so saddened\nby our failures that we almost gave up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225360,"text":"So why did we keep trying"},{"time":226720,"text":"when all the adults\nsaid it was impossible?"},{"time":229120,"text":"Well, maybe it's because we're kids.\nWe don't know any better."},{"time":232779,"text":"But the truth is, we kept trying\nbecause we thought it was still possible."},{"time":236280,"text":"We knew that if we were successful,"},{"time":238000,"text":"we would be helping the environment\nand making the world a better place."},{"time":241440,"text":"So we kept trying"},{"time":243120,"text":"and failing"},{"time":244880,"text":"and trying"},{"time":246560,"text":"and failing."},{"time":248160,"text":"We were so ready to give up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250640,"text":"But then it happened."},{"time":252240,"text":"With the right temperatures,\ntimes and chemicals,"},{"time":254960,"text":"we finally got that successful test result"},{"time":257240,"text":"showing us that we had created\nactivated carbon from Styrofoam waste."},{"time":261079,"text":"And at that moment,\nthe thing that had been impossible"},{"time":263680,"text":"all of a sudden wasn't."},{"time":265480,"text":"It showed us that although we had\nmany failures at the beginning,"},{"time":268560,"text":"we were able to persevere through them\nto get the test results that we wanted."},{"time":272280,"text":"And moreover, not only were we able\nto create activated carbon"},{"time":275240,"text":"for purifying water,"},{"time":276520,"text":"but we were also able\nto reduce Styrofoam waste,"},{"time":279000,"text":"solving two global problems\nwith just one solution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282320,"text":"So from then on, we were inspired\nto take our project further,"},{"time":285280,"text":"performing more tests\nto make it more effective"},{"time":287520,"text":"and testing it in real world situations."},{"time":289880,"text":"We then proceeded to receive funding"},{"time":291640,"text":"from the NSTA's eCYBERMISSION\nSTEM-in-Action program"},{"time":294640,"text":"sponsored by the US Army,"},{"time":296400,"text":"as well as FIRST Global Innovation Awards"},{"time":298800,"text":"sponsored by XPRIZE."},{"time":300640,"text":"And we were also honored"},{"time":301920,"text":"with the Scientific American\nInnovator Award"},{"time":304720,"text":"from Google Science Fair."},{"time":306480,"text":"And using these funds, we plan\nto file a full patent on our process"},{"time":309960,"text":"and to continue to work on our project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312440,"text":"So yes, although we started\nwith catching my dad's grill on fire"},{"time":316640,"text":"and failing so many times\nthat we almost quit,"},{"time":319160,"text":"it was well worth it\nwhen we look back at it now."},{"time":321720,"text":"We took a problem\nthat many people said was impossible"},{"time":324560,"text":"and we made it possible,"},{"time":326080,"text":"and we persevered when it looked\nlike nothing that we did would work."},{"time":329360,"text":"We learned that you can't have success"},{"time":331480,"text":"without a little,"},{"time":333000,"text":"or a lot, of failure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335440,"text":"So in the future, don't be afraid\nif your grill goes up in flames,"},{"time":339080,"text":"because you never know\nwhen your idea might just catch fire."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343800,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345040,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}